CERTIFICATE OF APPROVAL 
SECRETARIAL ELECTION 
KICKAPOO TRADITIONAL TRIBE OF TEXAS

 
 MARCH 22, 2017

I, Dan Deerinwater, Regional Director, Southern Plains Region, Bureau of Indian Affairs, by virtue of the 
authority granted to the Secretary of Interior by the Act of June 18, 1934, 48 Stat. 984, as amended, which 
was delegated to the Assistant Secretary - Indian Affairs by 209 DM 8.3 and redelegated by 3 IAM 4.4, do 
hereby approve the foregoing Amendment No. 1 to the Constitution of the Kickapoo Traditional Tribe of 
Texas. This amendment was duly adopted by a majority of the qualified voters who cast ballots in the 
March 22, 2017 election.

Dan Deerinwafer, Regional Director 
Southern Plains Region

4-12-17

Date

